This file describes major changes and important notes for each release.

# Version 1.0x1 (milestone 1.0x1)

This release is the first milestone for the Python version of prcs2hg.

## New feature

* It now tries to record simple merges in the converted Mercurial history.

## Known limitations

* It cannot convert merges with multiple merge parents very well.
* It may be confused by deleted versions.
